            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Theotecnii Bassi <lb n="2"/>Iunio Basso <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>comiti ordinis <lb n="4"/>primi vicario <lb n="5"/>urbis Romae <lb n="6"/>praefecto urbi <lb n="7"/>iudici sacrarum <lb n="8"/>cognitionum <lb n="9"/>filio Iuni Bassi <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimi</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>praefecti praeto<lb break="no" n="11"/>rio per annos <lb n="12"/>XIIII et consu<lb break="no" n="13"/>lis ordinari </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Dedicata <lb n="2"/>XV <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustas</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>divo Ioviano <lb n="4"/>et Varronia<lb break="no" n="5"/>no <expan><abbr>conss</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>An der Fundstelle Reste vermutlich einer römischen Villa. (B): Giardina: Z. 7/8: Zeilentrenner nicht angegeben; Giardina, AE 1964: Z. 9 (Ende): v. e.; Èvrard: Z. 16: Ioviano; AE 1964: Z. 16: Iovian[o]; Èvrard, AE 1964, Giardina: Z. 17/18: Varroni[a]/no.</p>
            </div>
